{"tid":2245003,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【物競天擇】早泄的好處","createTime":"2020-10-16T01:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T13:27:25.000Z","uid":163448,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d687d65913b00cfd670e41c481b78f8cbe76c4e1","tid":2245003,"uid":163448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"先唔講係物競天擇嘅世界早泄者得以繁殖嘅機率比較高<br />\n<br />\n早泄者把時間放在性愛的時間比較少<br />\n一來沒能力<br />\n二來較快能解決<br />\n<br />\n多咗嘅時間可以做咩？<br />\n<br />\n假設早泄者一分鐘完事<br />\n持久者要一小時<br />\n<br />\n早泄者每日有多59分鐘<br />\n一個月就29小時30分鐘<br />\n一年就有啲難計，總之好多時間<br />\n<br />\n之前有理論話花一萬小時就能成為專家<br />\n<a href=\"https://nicecasio.pixnet.net/blog/category/2831336#search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnicecasio.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fcategory%2F2831336%23search&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=95791b18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nicecasio.pixnet.net/blog/category/2831336#search</a><br />\n<br />\n早泄者已把多出的時間做訓練，不出三年就成為專家，可謂先天優勢。<br />\n<br />\n時間係無價，早泄者贏在起跑線"},{"pid":"e18d55ad8e0dee76170ce5e1a814351208bd97b7","tid":2245003,"uid":163448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:40:06.000Z","msg":"係優勢呀"},{"pid":"6610464d94f5d75558969640c2074d7c98a4c493","tid":2245003,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:53:04.000Z","msg":"唔夠人地咁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b3464f6e79ac78e11bde9deff24b5e8557c7b1","tid":2245003,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"假設早泄者一分鐘完事<br />\n持久者要一小時<br />\n<br />\n早泄者每日嘅快感比持久者少59分鐘<br />\n一個月就29小時30分鐘<br />\n一年就有啲難計，總之好多時間"},{"pid":"713d7811e1a1b729da9f46b97badf65c698828fd","tid":2245003,"uid":282438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T02:38:52.000Z","msg":"前戲呢? 調情呢?<br />\n如果直插咁有同強姦有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n其實你連呢少少時間都唔想浪費，咁不如連個1分鐘都慳返喇<br />\n咁咪可以再賺多1分鐘"},{"pid":"a949bab747c5